'''法斯蒂諾·阿斯普里拉'''（{{lang-en|Faustino Hernán "Tino" Asprilla Hinestroza}}，{{bd|1969年|11月10日|}}）是哥倫比亞足球運動員，以[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]身份效力於[[帕爾馬足球俱樂部|帕爾馬足球俱樂部]]、纽卡斯尔和[[哥倫比亞國家足球隊|哥倫比亞國家足球隊]]。

雖然他並非得分能手，但他是位迅速、敏捷、技巧純熟的球員，以他的天賦、創造力、力量和速度在球場上創造得分的機會並因此而聞名<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.espnstar.com/editorial/news/detail/item704033/Asprilla's-magical-European-night|title=Asprilla's magical European night|publisher=ESPN|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111122081738/http://www.espnstar.com/editorial/news/detail/item704033/Asprilla%27s-magical-European-night/|archivedate=2011-11-22|accessdate=2022-01-07}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.orlandosentinel.com/1994-06-15/features/9406150766_1_baggio-great-soccer-players-goals-in-world|title=Baggio Takes Great Strides Toward Soccer Greatness|publisher=The Orlando Sentinel|author1=Mike Zizzo|date=15 June 1994|accessdate=24 September 2015|archive-date=2015-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151114003756/http://articles.orlandosentinel.com/1994-06-15/features/9406150766_1_baggio-great-soccer-players-goals-in-world|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除了球技之外、他在球場上及球場外的表現也引起一些爭議。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://fourfourtwo.com/news/southamerica/78575/default.aspx|title=Falcao form boosts troubled Colombia|publisher=FourFourTwo|date=29 April 2011|accessdate=2017-01-16|archive-date=2012-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120628015102/http://fourfourtwo.com/news/southamerica/78575/default.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.footballfancast.com/2009/12/football-blogs/happened-faustino-asprilla|title=Whatever happened to Newcastle’s Faustino Asprilla?|publisher=FootballFanCast|date=31 December 2009|accessdate=2017-01-16|archive-date=2012-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120807100712/http://www.footballfancast.com/2009/12/football-blogs/happened-faustino-asprilla|dead-url=no}}</ref>

